Pantera's Corp said it agreed tobuy ten pizza restaurants in southeastern Colorado fromcreditors foreclosing on the facilities.    The purchase price includes 1.25 mln dlrs in cash andcompany stock, it said.    Separately, Pantera's said it issued an area developmentagreement with a franchisee group for northeastern Colorado,including the Denver area, for the opening of about 20franchised Pantera's pizza restaurants. Reuter&#3;